Automatic White Correction
----------------------------
Automatic white correction on images (both 8-bit and 16-bit).

Algorithm
image pixel with max value P(r+g+b)

if the image is 16-bit

then for every RED, GREEN and BLUE band of image
old=P(band)
new=(65535)*old/new
P(band)=new


if the image is 8-bit

then for every RED, GREEN and BLUE band of image
old=P(band)
new=(255)*old/new
P(band)=new

The resultant image as correct white balancing of pixels.